sequenceDiagram
  actor C as Customer
  participant W as WebApp
  participant P as PaymentService
  participant G as PaymentGateway
  participant D as Database

  C->>W: Checkout (select payment method)
  W->>P: POST /payments/authorize (orderId, amount, token)
  P->>D: checkIdempotency(orderId, idempotencyKey)
  D-->>P: no existing transaction

  P->>G: POST /authorize (amount, currency, paymentToken)
  G-->>P: authorized (transactionId, authCode)
  P->>D: INSERT transaction (transactionId, amount, status="Authorized", timestamp)

  P-->>W: payment authorized (transactionId)
  W-->>C: "Payment confirmed"

  alt Payment Declined
    G-->>P: declined (reason)
    P->>D: INSERT transaction (status="Declined", reason)
    P-->>W: payment declined
    W-->>C: "Payment declined: [reason]"
  else Gateway Timeout
    G-->>P: timeout (10s)
    P->>P: retryOnce (same idempotencyKey)
    G-->>P: timeout (10s)
    P->>D: INSERT transaction (status="Pending")
    P-->>W: payment pending
    W-->>C: "Payment processing. Check order status later."
  end
